messages.text: Great! I’m inside but I’ll go out.
You sure? Is the line long?
Yeah, there’s a lot of people.
What do you expect, it’s Halloween.
I’ll get some drinks while you’re still in line.
Yeah he’s already inside with me
Got us two lemon drop shots :)
Are you still at the bar?
No, waiting in line at the bathroom with a few of the girls.
Okay, just wait at the bar.
Sorry, you know how Halloween parties are.
Uhhh, this dude keeps following me.
When I went to the bathroom, he was behind me.
Now that I’m out, he’s like creeping behind me still.
He’s probably just looking for his friends like you are.
Making my way to the bar now.
No worries, everyone is just waiting here.
Shay, this dude is seriously freaking me out.
He has this creepy mask on too.
Has painted blood across the mouth of it, the eyes are colored pitch black.
How do you know he’s following you?
I made a few turns here and there and he did the same.
Also when I turned and looked at him he acted like he was doing something else.
It’s Halloween the creep is probably just looking to scare you.
Where are you, are you near the bar? We can try looking for you.
If you leave, I’ll probably make it over and then you’ll be the ones lost.
Don’t want to go around in circles.
Yeah.. should I say something, this dude is giving me the creeps.
If it really bothers you then yeah if not still make your way to the bar.
Sorry people are all squished together it's hard to walk through.
What the hell? Are you okay?
He just grabbed my arm and did this creepy smile.
Trying to find you guys now.
Okay, want us to look for you?
That way we won’t all be lost.
The guy isn’t around so I think I scared him off.
Does he have his phone on him?
Just other people in their costumes.
Creep probably went to bother someone else.
Hope so, don’t want to see that weirdo again.
By the way, what is Josh wearing?
Oh, I’m sure you’ll know when you see him.
Are you staying in one certain spot?
I’m near the second dance floor.
Okay, Josh should be there soon.
I just want to find you guys already so we can hang out.
With the mask, he’s walking towards me.
Guess dude didn’t get the hint.
Great timing for him not to have his phone.
Just calm down it's probably just some loser trying to mess with you.
I’m gonna see what is up with this guy.
Find out who he is yet?
Josh took the mask off, it was him the entire time!
Hope we didn’t scare you too bad.
